WAP::wmls - WAP WMLScript compiler

Description:
------------
    The script 'wmlsc' is the compiler.
    The script 'wmlsd' is a dissassembler.

    The parser is generated by Parse::Yapp.

    The compiler could be parametrized by the file 'wmlslibs.cfg' 
    what contains all the description of known libraries.

    WAP Specifications are available on <http://www.wapforum.org/>.

Prerequisites:
--------------
    This module needs Perl 5.8.


Build/Installation:
-------------------
    Standard build/installation supported by ExtUtils::MakeMaker(3)...
	$ perl Makefile.PL
	$ make
	$ make install


Send bug reports, comments and suggestions to francois.perrad@gadz.org
